code: import axios from"axios";import{baseURL}from"./constants";export class SiteUserController{static async getAll(){const respone=await axios.get("".concat(baseURL,"/siteUsers/getAll"));return respone.data;}static async createSiteUser(siteUserDTO){const respone=await axios.post("".concat(baseURL,"/siteUsers/createUser"),siteUserDTO);return respone.data;}static async updateSiteUser(siteUserDTO){const respone=await axios.patch("".concat(baseURL,"/siteUsers/updateUser"),siteUserDTO);return respone.data;}static async deleteSiteUser(siteUserDTO){const respone=await axios.delete("".concat(baseURL,"/siteUsers/deleteUser"),{data:siteUserDTO});return respone.data;}}
